{"tid":2435215,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"窗邊聽歌手機不慎飛出窗　土耳其16歲少年為撿手機墮樓12層死亡","createTime":"2021-03-06T05:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:02:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e7695f0e7449feb908477b90933319b07f848e","tid":2435215,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"土耳其日前發生一宗墜樓悲劇。一名16歲少年坐在窗邊聽歌用電話時，電話不小心飛出窗外，為了及時撿回空中的電話，少年不小心失去平衡，直墮12層樓，最終傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，事發於當地1日下午2點30分左右，16歲少年Ismail Ababey被發現從高處墜樓，身受重傷。警方考慮到少年耳朵裏有耳機，相信意外是因為他獨自在家中坐在窗邊聽歌及使用電話，沒想到電話不小心飛出窗外，為了要撿回飛在空中的電話，不小心失去平衡，從12樓窗邊直墮地面。<br />\n<br />\n據閉路電視畫面，Ismail Ababey從高空極速墜落地面，一名路人發現後馬上衝上前了解，只見他傷勢相當嚴重，倒臥血泊中，但仍有生命跡象。醫護人員接報後趕到現場急救，但送醫後不幸宣佈不治。<br />\n<br />\n目前土耳其警方已針對意外展開調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2894385/fall_thumb_20210306_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2894385%2Ffall_thumb_20210306_S_1024.jpg&h=7994510e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f8babf75b888b25f624ca15f68de2e7329467b1","tid":2435215,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"點撚樣「電話不小心飛出窗外」呀 ?<br />\n<br />\n似自殺喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96a83befda5bffd3ba03b6819a7281cc94974bb","tid":2435215,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"被自殺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e29c6c7e73078d04c71673c2c7b41c7d9f3ad59","tid":2435215,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnshS3K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnshS3K.gif&h=57ff9be7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"772834ab521c2aa55fa85567cef03f491956ec6f","tid":2435215,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike"